02/13/85 bce

Syntax as a command:  bce


Function:  causes BCE to be entered.  All Multics operation is
suspended.  When the system is in trouble, it is sometimes necessary to
enter BCE to use the dump or probe commands.  This command can be used
in ring 1 or ring 4.


Notes:  This command should be used only at the direction of the system
programming staff, as it causes disruption of service to users.  Under
some circumstances, it can cause interactive users to be disconnected.
